Groove LightTango

AllTracks SeqRnd Off

Drum-Kick  	     Sequence   *     *     *    D1
Drum-Snare       Sequence   *     *     D8   D12
Drum-PHH         Sequence   *     *     *    D13
Drum-Tam         Sequence   *     *     *    D13
