Groove LightTango

SeqSize 1

Bass             Sequence     B11
Bass-Piano       Sequence     -
Chord-Accordion  Sequence     C13
Chord-Guitar     Sequence     C13
Drum-Clave       Sequence     -
Drum-Kick        Sequence     D13
Drum-PHH         Sequence     {D123; D12 Shift .5}
Drum-Snare       Sequence     D1
Drum-Tam         Sequence     -

